Typescript Types #

Typescript Types modules are used for type-checking throughout VueVentus components and modules.

BaseFunction #

Import #

javascript
import type { BaseFunction } from '@obewds/vueventus'
1

Module Code #

ts
// ./src/types/BaseFunction.ts

export type BaseFunction = () => string
